 Reddy's, Kotak Mahindra. IT sector fell 1.4%, PSU Bank index rose 1.3%; volatility persists.","url":"https://www.moneycontrol.com/news/business/markets/stock-market-live-updates-gift-nifty-indicates-a-weak-start-us-markets-fall-asia-gains-liveblog-13840454.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-24T06:33:00","source":"Moneycontrol"},{"id":"260222158929833","title":"PSBs surpass private banks as quarterly profits reach new highs.\nOnly 3 of 30 listed universal banks had >1% net NPAs in Q3.","summary":"PSBs surpass private banks as quarterly profits reach new highs.\nOnly 3 of 30 listed universal banks had >1% net NPAs in Q3.","url":"https://www.business-standard.com/opinion/columns/psbs-outperform-private-peers-yet-again-as-quarterly-profits-hit-new-high-126022200380_1.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-22T15:50:37","source":"Business Standard"},{"id":"260219157215952","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank saw a 37.1% surge in derivatives open interest on 19 Feb 2026.\nDespite the spike, the stock underperformed its sector and broader indices.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank saw a 37.1% surge in derivatives open interest on 19 Feb 2026.\nDespite the spike, the stock underperformed its sector and broader indices.","url":"https://www.marketsmojo.com/news/stocks-in-action/kotak-mahindra-bank-sees-sharp-surge-in-derivatives-open-interest-amid-mixed-price-action-3847291","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-19T15:00:29","source":"Marketsmojo"},{"id":"260219156810893","title":"New M&A funding norms present $15B opportunity for banks with strong investment banking capabilities.\nKey changes include 75% acquisition financing, 3:1 debt-equity ratio, and doubled finance cap to 20% of Tier 1 capital.","summary":"New M&A funding norms present $15B opportunity for banks with strong investment banking capabilities.\nKey changes include 75% acquisition financing, 3:1 debt-equity ratio, and doubled finance cap to 20% of Tier 1 capital.","url":"https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/stocks/news/ma-funding-norms-open-up-a-15-b-opportunity-for-banks/articleshow/128532445.cms","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-19T00:00:00","source":"The Economic Times"},{"id":"502270","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank appoints Ramesh Iyer as Independent Director for 4 years from Feb 17, 2026, succeeding Dr. Ashok Gulati.\nIyer, with over 40 years in Mahindra Group, has held key roles and won multiple industry awards like Ernst & Young Entrepreneur of the Year.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank appoints Ramesh Iyer as Independent Director for 4 years from Feb 17, 2026, succeeding Dr. Ashok Gulati.\nIyer, with over 40 years in Mahindra Group, has held key roles and won multiple industry awards like Ernst & Young Entrepreneur of the Year.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/business/companies/kotak-mahindra-bank-appoints-ramesh-iyer-as-independent-director-ashok-gulati-to-retire-in-march-ws-l-19852338.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-17T22:48:12","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"260215154330483","title":"RBI's revised guidelines on acquisition financing enable Indian banks like SBI, Bank of India, and Kotak Mahindra Bank to participate in M&A, refinancing, and stake hikes with eased equity requirements.\nThe new norms allow unlisted firms with Rs 500 crore net worth and 3-year profitability to access financing, boosting domestic consolidation and capex in sectors like manufacturing and healthcare.","summary":"RBI's revised guidelines on acquisition financing enable Indian banks like SBI, Bank of India, and Kotak Mahindra Bank to participate in M&A, refinancing, and stake hikes with eased equity requirements.\nThe new norms allow unlisted firms with Rs 500 crore net worth and 3-year profitability to access financing, boosting domestic consolidation and capex in sectors like manufacturing and healthcare.","url":"https://www.financialexpress.com/business/banking-finance/banks-to-drive-domestic-mampa-as-rbi-eases-financing-norms/4143843/","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-15T19:07:00","source":"Financial Express"},{"id":"493053","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank executed Rs. 103.3 crore NSE block trade for 2,459,567 shares.\nThe trade occurred at Rs. 420 per share, reflecting significant transaction volume.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank executed Rs. 103.3 crore NSE block trade for 2,459,567 shares.\nThe trade occurred at Rs. 420 per share, reflecting significant transaction volume.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-13T14:48:37","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"260209150298186","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank CTO Bhavnish Lathia resigns citing personal reasons.\nNilesh Chaudhari takes over as CTO; Lathia's last day was February 9.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank CTO Bhavnish Lathia resigns citing personal reasons.\nNilesh Chaudhari takes over as CTO; Lathia's last day was February 9.","url":"https://www.business-standard.com/companies/people/kotak-bank-cto-bhavnish-lathia-resigns-nilesh-chaudhari-appointed-126020901550_1.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T21:25:13","source":"Business Standard"},{"id":"480680","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank to meet investors at Axis Capital's Advantage India Conference on Feb 12, 2026.\nThe meeting is disclosed under SEBI Regulation 30 for investor information and dissemination.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank to meet investors at Axis Capital's Advantage India Conference on Feb 12, 2026.\nThe meeting is disclosed under SEBI Regulation 30 for investor information and dissemination.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=4015d95f-361e-43e3-83d5-4fc461796b1b.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T18:09:09","source":"BSE"}]}]